<h1>美国国会大厦骚乱者因电击枪袭击被判12年徒刑</h1>
<p>Author: 半岛电视台＋通讯社</p>
<p>Publisher: Al Jazeera</p>
<p>Published Time: 2023-06-22T02:38:44</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-06-22T02:38:44</p>
<p>Description: 丹尼尔·罗德里格斯在因1月6日骚乱而被判最长刑期之一后戏剧性地退出法庭。</p>
<p>Images: ["<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1687400453.jpg">1-1687400453.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-1687400464.jpg">2-1687400464.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-1687400469.jpg">3-1687400469.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/4-1687400481.jpg">4-1687400481.jpg</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/5-1687400488.jpg">5-1687400488.jpg</a>"]</p>
